but what makes voodoo so interesting is this vibrant relationship between the living and the dead .
the living gave birth to the spirits .
the spirits can be complained by under the great water , answers to the rhythm of dance , to deny the soul of the living temporary , so that the akolyth for a short shiny moment becomes the god .
