nathaniel left juilliard , suffered a breakdown , and 30 years later he lived as homeless people on the streets of skid row at the center of los angeles .
i recommend all of you to read steves book or to see the movie so that not only did you understand the wonderful connection that was born between these two men , but also how music helped make that connection , and how it was the instrument when that word game is allowed to get the mithalf , nathaniel &apos;s way off the street .
i met mr ayers in 2008 , two years ago , in walt disney smooth hall .
