the idea behind the stuxnet computer worm is pretty simple .
we don &apos;t want iran to build the bomb .
the most important one there for developing nuclear weapons is the uranium incentive facility in natance .
the gray boxes you see here , these are real-time control systems .
now , if we can commit the systems that control twists and valves , we can actually do a lot of problems with the centrifuge .
these gray boxes don &apos;t walk with windows software ; they &apos;re based on a completely different technology .
